# Server Configuration Rules

## Express Setup
- Use Express static middleware to serve all files from project root
- Default port: 3000 (configurable via PORT environment variable
- Enable CORS and proper headers for development

## Route Structure
- `/` → [home.html](mdc:home.html)
- `/about` → [about.html](mdc:about.html)  
- `/game` → [game.html](mdc:game.html)
- `/canvas` → [canvas.html](mdc:canvas.html)

## Error Handling
- 404 handler for unmatched routes
- Proper HTTP status codes
- Graceful error responses

## Development Features
- Console logging for server startup
- Hot reload support (if using nodemon)
- Static file serving for assets (CSS, JS, images)